  <a href="https://coltrane.readthedocs.io"><h1 align="center">coltrane</h1></a>
</p>
<p align="center">A minimal app framework for content sites üéµ</p>

![PyPI](https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/coltrane?color=blue&style=flat-square)
